Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:06.55,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,0)\pos(1366,531)}BRING ON A WAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,古宾嫩商业工会联合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:08.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,位于距离奥尔特海上500连德的海上岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:08.25,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：连德，异世界距离单位。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是商人集合国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:17.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,由七个巨大工会运营的海洋半主权国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而领导他们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:23.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏依洛克商会及夏依洛克银行的大首领
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,古宾嫩联合水军的水师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放荡不羁却有能之子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:31.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,班赛尔马欣夏依洛克八世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:36.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,普利冈特商店首席职员 普利冈特银行首领
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,联合水军的军监师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:43.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑冷静内心更加冰冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:45.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,纳伊赛尔普利冈特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有一位漂流者来到了他们的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:55.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,准提督 大日本帝国海军联合舰队少将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:01:00.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者 山口多闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能合你口味就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是从西方订购和「米饭」很相似的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,光那里一碗的价值就和一艘商船相当
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:13.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有些由大陆的魔术师们制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:17.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让大豆腐烂变成臭粥的不明物体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这片海上已经几乎成为了「我们就是海洋」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:26.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特海军已经几乎被完全消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:30.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有任何能阻碍我们海上霸权的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「我们就是海洋」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:39.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真动听 古宾嫩的愿望终于在这里实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能够这么快决定这个趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫骑兵归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,允许着舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:02:00.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都多亏了多闻殿下所指导的海上机动舰队的巨大功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我什么都不干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也会夺取这片海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,您谦虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们接下来打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:13.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打算进军奥尔特本土乘胜追击么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们虽然在海上所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在陆地上……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说我们只是鱼龙混杂的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,并不拥有进军奥尔特的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:27.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把奥尔特抢过来也无法维持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不经济
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,经营那些穷人们的领地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一点好处都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现今对于已经掌握的海上通商权利的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所追求的是与奥尔特的和平共处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果奥尔特答应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们也是不得不答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:51.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其后如果奥尔特一如既往地像其他国家发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要向奥尔特或者敌国贩卖物资
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特在陨落的那天以前依然是我们的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是正确的海洋国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,商业大国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们武运亨隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要回去那艘铁船的残骸上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候住在我们这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会为你准备好住宅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,超豪华的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:33.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 那里才能让我最安心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还不打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个 把「飞龙」交给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后都没有把军帽脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他到现在都没有相信过我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过很多次了 夏依洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须接手那艘飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:05.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是其他世界中令人惊叹的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在还不能惹怒多闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么想要的东西就告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会立刻送过来的 提督大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:36.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会交出来的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:48.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国海军 就只剩下我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------OP------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个修不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且越看越奇怪这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像是折叠过 到底有多少层啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.17,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：折叠锻打法，古时兵器常用锻打法。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}二万 三万吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:39.01,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1812,551)}变态啊 真是变态的作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.01,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(34,529)}变态啊 变态国度的作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:42.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎样才能研磨到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.12,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1812,537)}这到底是钢材还是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我还听说矮人是冶炼的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原来做不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在小瞧我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:04.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰已经很熟练地指示矮人族了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们都是一个样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,相比这个 问题是奥尔特的残存兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西方的第三军团和第四军团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:19.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说断绝了帝国对他们的物资援助让他们显现出疲态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正面交锋的话还是会吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,两个军团的指挥官关系怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽想这么说 其实很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说过什么坏传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:38.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不怎么好才对 至少现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多个相同程度的军团存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且处于没有中央统治的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会相互争夺主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂人妖 以你的名义给双方写书信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,内容由我来写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:57.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且与一 我有件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帝都被袭击了 这个消息属实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是古宾嫩干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:07.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是称作黑王军的怪物军团干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被圣日尔曼伯爵的军队所击退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是帝都的损害也十分严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特指挥部也处于被摧毁的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼伯爵也无法完全收拾残局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是个是男是女都不知道的弱不禁风文人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能干得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他恢复了空缺几十年的「国父」一职
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,计划让第三军团或者第四军团的将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,接受这个地位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复国家的威严还有秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然恢复「国父」的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼的使者在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:51.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正准备前往第四军团的将军列米克处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,立即前往帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再组织一支队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼的使者先来到这里只是侥幸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:05.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「国父」一职怎么能交给基古门提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家加快脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到马腹也撕烂为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,列米克将军 前方有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是第三军团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个障碍是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要阻挡我们的去路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,疯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我们基古门提将军将会成为国父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道别动部队是不是很顺利地消灭他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经预先稳固了最短路程的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:44.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第四军团也可能像我们一样派遣了别动部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请径直前往帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啊 我就是国父了 就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全员带着头巾 无法分辨是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:05.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,基古门提真狡猾 很小心谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根据骑兵的配置就能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被骑兵队伍无意识保护着的就是将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准喉部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,距离太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是等到距离接近后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第三军团的伪装就会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:41.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:50.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嚎叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是第四军团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:57.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:06.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那种距离还能射中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样第三军团和第四军团都失去了各自的将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,处于独立并开始相互争斗的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 书信大作战第二回合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给战争中的西方诸侯们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,送去讲和或者说休战的申请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:39.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼 给出怎么的条件那些家伙才会答应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是持续了五十年的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的确也是十分疲乏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:50.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对我们的憎恨也是在不断地积累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看来需要些土特产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把占领的西方领地全部归还
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那些土地现在仍然由第三第四军团把守着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第三第四军团已经疲惫不堪而且断绝了补给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了将领 陷入了反目的大混乱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是击溃他们并夺回领地绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把这一情报泄露给西方诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们当做给西方的祭品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使放着不管也是互相残杀后毁灭的军团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么至少不要让他们白白死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是为了获得兵力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么对付黑王军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不付出代价就获得兵力的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逃离了中央统治的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能这么简单归属于我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:53.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,外来人要获取兵力的方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是吸收残兵败将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们为了得到军团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就不得不把这个军团完全击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果拖到第三第四军团内乱至毁灭状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西方诸侯再趁势进攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西方就会获得全面胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后残存的兵力少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,此时这些家伙才不会答应所谓的休战请求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快想想 现在就让西方攻打过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虚称与古宾嫩成功议和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:27.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夸大漂流者和我们军队的壮大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托十月机关骗他们说「黑王下一个目标是西方诸侯」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再虚张声势说「我们马上派援军去西方 不要打过来」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:40.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就…就应该…怎么样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是谎话和虚张声势嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要让我来统筹这些工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是在玩拼图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:52.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能做到的 圣日尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,击溃两个军团 再打击西方那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能获得军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,议和也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就暂且试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么我才不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是试一下即使失败了都不是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然会去试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得像是那些废人小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,赌博的钱全都输光了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:26.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是人渣小白脸要被捅了的情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在臭水沟里发现尸体的情节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用两封信就消灭两个军团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这男人是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,迷上我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有 我对胡子没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰那家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:50.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又到处游荡 他的伤口行不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的大将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 那是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 不能看他们 不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好无聊啊 老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好无聊啊 饭还没做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,呆在这里没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹是大将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里发呆真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信和人妖在讨论各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是完全听不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从十二岁开始我就只知道上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:34.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个功名饿鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是当大将的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 信他不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:43.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,织田信长不是我们能比的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定比父亲还有叔父还要高明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我被扔到这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有离开关原来到这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:58.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是要让我再干一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要确实用我的生命来帮他达成伟业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.76,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：丰久在乌头坂舍命拖住敌人让将领逃脱。（见第一话）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乌头坂还没完结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:11.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不行啊小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人虽了不起但危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的男人心中养着一只魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必然养着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:26.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那个男人之前有何成就 有何失败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他是有相当能力的大将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的魔物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你和与一都是一把锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:40.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把锁打开 心中的魔物再次出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的魔与他的魔将会开始相互争夺这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界就会变成血腥的修罗场一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:52.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你恢复正常了吗 老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快住手 他要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}巴尔巴尔巴尔巴尔巴尔干半岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:02.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}越过阿尔卑斯 他们还距离三百sicle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:08.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抽得挺香的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的给我一根吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这大叔真扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说在前头我们不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:26.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是带来了个有事找你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:37.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是魔术协会「十月机关」的统领
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在下安倍晴明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,安倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:43.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:48.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这真叫人的惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:53.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到古宾嫩还派了普利冈特过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到居然会派排名第二的重要人员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:59.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,过来进行第一次的议和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他们也想表明与我们进行议和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不能好好解决这边的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西方的策略就会前功尽弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必须全神贯注在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是排名第二的普利冈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是地位最高的夏依洛特商会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:26.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,班赛尔马欣 夏依洛克八世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:30.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,简单的事物要尽早并直接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们商会的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的对话更加简单明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:38.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是处于交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:44.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,该说你不知天高地厚还是笨蛋一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要动我一根汗毛都会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让奥尔特上下国民都饿死而至
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那样子毫无死角的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除了那张脸全让人十分讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除了脸以外一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 别这样说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你们想要投降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是议和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论选哪一边都没那么容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争本来就是你们先发动的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们屡战屡胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一边倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也准备推进奥尔特的内陆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:28.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对于完全没有占领统治和陆军指挥经验的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全不可能会去冒这个风险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把这场战争继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们来说完全没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:41.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,商人本质的你们是不会这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:47.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来把军舰转换为商船就能赚到多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:51.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来把海军的人数削弱就能省下多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使赚到了五枚金币
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:00.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也会想着「原本能赚十枚的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想着亏了五枚而不是赚了五枚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能这样想的就只有你们这些商人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就想着议和对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无死角的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不接受任何赔偿要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,白纸和平协议 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能这么厚颜无耻地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们的海军还有海上的商人都被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大海不仅仅属于你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有吧 圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:51.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下就把粮食物资之类的东西和钱借给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还处于交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:59.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们向敌人交出粮食还有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也调查过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王从北方压过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:09.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首当其冲的是我们奥尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界被毁坏了的话我们也做不成生意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想让我们帮助奥尔特变强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:21.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说这是提前购买不如说是前期投资
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:25.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的奥尔特拥有来自异世界的漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:30.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救世界后 金钱什么的都会换给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有用于典当的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能让战争一边倒 漂流者的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族的力量加上精灵族的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:56.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加上人族的热情加上漂流者的头脑的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:02.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它 消灭了黑王军的先遣部队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是人类的热情 其实主要是粪便
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有家畜的……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:09.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,最后说的大便什么的完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:10.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,产生爆发力的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:15.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,渗入大小便经过长年累月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在化学和微生物的作用下产生强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:23.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:25.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:29.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘记你也是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:35.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一定程度上量产着这种铁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:39.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就特别地批发卖给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你们就贩卖这些铁炮赚大钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是提督所说的「枪」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这就是漂流者们的世界的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:54.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是进入奥尔特的漂流者们所持的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有想过我们也会复制和量产
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:05.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后不再依赖你们的可能性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:07.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:08.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会制造的吧 光是制作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:15.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟都是由些简单的东西构成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们能做到不赔本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:21.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪身是由矮人族冶炼而成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:26.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪托把和铁块研磨精细活是由精灵族的木工完成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:30.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正是有他们在才能快速量产出来的产品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:34.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有你们怎么也得不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,粪便和畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:39.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我们是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:44.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个兵器是通过火药让子弹射出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:50.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火药的原料是木炭 硫磺还有硝石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在还没有发现硝石矿产的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:58.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能通过家畜圈和住户厕所的地下获得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:03.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有拥有众多人口农村和家畜的大小便
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:08.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作人口帝国的奥尔特才能制作出来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:11.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对于你们这个新兴的海上商人公会联合国家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:15.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使竭尽全力也是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:17.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:20.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所积累的粪便量可是天差地别
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.59,0:24:26.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是矮人族的力量和精灵族的技术加上人类的粪便的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:29.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,交易成立
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:32.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:33.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大首领
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.25,0:24:36.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就把粮食还有资金借给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:38.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,利息一点也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.35,0:24:41.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王要攻打过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:47.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不让衰弱的奥尔特振兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.39,0:24:53.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了吗 圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------ed-------------------
