Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.19,0:26:39.56,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,The outlandish Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:05:00.33,difters-op,,0,0,0,,发动引擎 给我动力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:04.79,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油门 奏响福音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:05.50,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:05.50,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:19.27,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.19,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:25.69,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.86,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.24,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.70,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.54,difters-op,,0,0,0,,即使已超速 也无法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:44.29,difters-op,,0,0,0,,引擎全开 全身绷紧
